Wow, Zildrax. I did not think i would ever say this, but.. i agree. In part, that is. Of course, i dont care wether you claim it is Cazic Thule, who is not denied, or wether it is the big bad lizzard in the sky. But you have a *very* valid point. Multiple nations truly cannot exist. So, all Norrath should succumb to hate, and let itself be ruled by hatred.<br>
<br>
The part i dont agree to is that all of us see Norrath as a peaceful place. It is a chaotic swirling maelstrom of hatred. Or, most of it is. Many you call 'softskins' see this, and enjoy it. I do. Hopefully, all will be, in time. Even the Iksar will succumb to it - or become extinct.<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>  <br>
